.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Snoop-Dogg-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Snoop-Dogg-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Snoop-Dogg-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据宣布，<a href="/artists/Snoop-Dogg">史努比狗狗</a>将在穿越法国的最后几个小时里传递奥运火炬。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/mount-westmore-snoop-cube-40-short-review-snoop-dogg-ice-cube-e40-too-short-g-funk-3364110">Mount Westmore –“Snoop，Cube，40，$hort”评论：说唱超级团体充满了想法和个性</a></li></ul><p>这位《Gin and Juice》说唱歌手将在周五（7 月 26 日）巴黎 2024 年奥运会开幕式之前担任奥运圣火的最后火炬手之一。史努比将在法兰西奥林匹克体育场所在的圣但尼的街道上传递火炬。</p><p>法国说唱歌手 MC Solaar、法国女演员 Laetitia Casta 和退役乌克兰撑杆跳运动员谢尔盖·布勃卡 (Sergey Bubka) 也将与 Snoop 一起担任仪式的火炬手。圣火将从那里前往巴黎市中心杜乐丽花园的奥运圣火台，这是 2024 年奥运会期间的最终目的地。最终谁将结束为期数周的奥运会接力之旅尚未揭晓。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C9ww6FUI2u5/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 6